            .intro__client__review
              .intro__review__client 
                img(src="/images/r2.png" alt="")
              .intro__review__content__details
                .intro__reviews__client__details Georgette Arrey Taku 
                .intro__review__text__details
                  p Pochi is so passionate and committed in helping communities, amplifying the voices of the vulnerable, giving them the chance to tell their untold stories.  will recommend her again and will work with her anytime the opportunity comes up again.

            .intro__client__review
              .intro__review__client 
                img(src="/images/r4.png" alt="")
              .intro__review__content__details
                .intro__reviews__client__details Anastassia White 
                .intro__review__text__details
                  p Our students enjoyed the interactive session Pochi facilitated and were left energized to continue their peacebuilding practice!


          .cta
            .btn
              a(href='/reviews')
                span See more

      section.connect
        .intro__connect
          .intro__connect__title
            h2 Let's connect
          .intro__connect__cta 
            p Get to know me and let's work together
            br
            br
            br
            br
            .cta
              .btn
                a(href='/contact')
                  span Let's connect
      +footer 
